quran[23]{c,v,t,f}:
  51,52,"Báyẹn ni (ọ̀rọ̀ ṣe rí)! Òjíṣẹ́ kan kò wá bá àwọn tó ṣíwájú wọn àfi kí wọ́n wí pé: “Òpìdán tàbí wèrè ni.”",""
  51,53,"Ṣé wọn sọ àsọọ́lẹ̀ nípa rẹ̀ láààrin ara wọn ni? Rárá o! Ìjọ olùtayọ-ẹnu-ààlà ni wọ́n ni.",""
  51,54,"Nítorí náà, ṣẹ́rí kúrò lọ́dọ̀ wọn ná. Ìwọ kì í ṣe ẹni tí A máa bá wí.",""
  51,55,"Ṣèrántí nítorí pé, dájúdájú ìrántí máa wúlò fún àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo.",""
  51,56,"Àti pé Èmi kò ṣẹ̀dá àlùjànnú àti ènìyàn bí kò ṣe pé kí wọ́n lè jọ́sìn fún Mi.",""
  51,57,"Èmi kò gbèrò arísìkí kan láti ọ̀dọ̀ wọn. Èmi kò sì gbèrò pé kí wọ́n máa bọ́ Mi.",""
  51,58,"Dájúdájú Allāhu, Òun ni Olùpèsè, Alágbára líle.",""
  51,59,"Dájúdájú ìpín ìyà tí ó máa jẹ àwọn tó ṣàbòsí (wọ̀nyí) ni irú ìpín ìyà tí ó jẹ ìjọ ẹlẹ́ṣẹ̀ (irú) wọn. Nítorí náà, kí wọ́n má ṣe kán Mi lójú (nípa ìyà wọn).",""
  51,60,"Nítorí náà, ègbé ni fún àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ ní ọjọ́ wọn tí À ń ṣe ní àdéhùn fún wọn.",""
  52,1,"Allāhu fi àpáta Tūr búra.",""
  52,2,"Ó tún fi Tírà tí wọ́n kọ n̄ǹkan sínú rẹ̀ búra .",""
  52,3,"(Wọ́n kọ̀ ọ́) sínú n̄ǹkan ìkọ̀wé tí wọ́n tẹ́ ojú rẹ̀ sílẹ̀.",""
  52,4,"Allāhu fi Ilé tí àwọn mọlāika ń wọnú rẹ̀ ní ojoojúmọ́ nínú sánmọ̀ búra.",""
  52,5,"Ó tún fi àjà tí wọ́n gbé sókè (ìyẹn, sánmọ̀) búra.",""
  52,6,"Ó tún fi agbami odò tí wọ́n máa mú iná jáde nínú rẹ̀ búra.",""
  52,7,"Dájúdájú ìyà Olúwa rẹ máa ṣẹlẹ̀.",""
  52,8,"Kò sí ẹni tí ó máa dènà rẹ̀.",""
  52,9,"(Ó máa ṣẹlẹ̀) ní ọjọ́ tí sánmọ̀ máa mì tìtì tààrà.",""
  52,10,"àpáta sì máa rìn lọ dànù.",""
  52,11,"Ní ọjọ́ yẹn, ègbé ni fún àwọn tó pe òdodo ní irọ́,",""
  52,12,"àwọn tí wọ́n wà nínú ìsọkúsọ, tí wọ́n ń ṣeré.",""
  52,13,"(Rántí) ọjọ́ tí wọn yóò máa tì wọ́n lọ́ sínú iná Jahanamọ ní ìtìkutì.",""
  52,14,"Èyí ni Iná náà tí ẹ̀ ń pè ní irọ́.",""
